    "It's extremely rare that you encounter this issue! Make sure that your TrollStore installation or jailbroken environment is properly configured.\n\nYou may use the browser without JIT temporarily until the next launch by activating JIT-Less Mode." : {
      "comment" : "Paragraph break intentional",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "It's extremely rare that you encounter this issue! Make sure that your TrollStore installation or jailbroken environment is properly configured.\n\nYou may use the browser without JIT temporarily until the next launch by activating JIT-Less Mode."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Il est très rare de rencontrer ce problème! Assurez-vous que votre installation de TrollStore ou que votre environnement de jailbreak est configuré correctement.\n\nVous devrez peut-être utiliser le navigateur sans JIT temporairement jusqu'au prochain démarrage en activant le mode JITless."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "极少会出现此问题！请确保你的 TrollStore 安装或越狱环境配置正确。\n\n在下次启动前，你可以通过启用无 JIT 模式，暂时在不使用 JIT 的情况下使用浏览器。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
