    "Please check that your pairing file is valid, your loopback VPN is on, and you're connected to a stable Wi-Fi network.\n\nYou may use the browser without JIT temporarily until the next launch by activating JIT-Less Mode." : {
      "comment" : "Paragraph break intentional",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Please check that your pairing file is valid, your loopback VPN is on, and you're connected to a stable Wi-Fi network.\n\nYou may use the browser without JIT temporarily until the next launch by activating JIT-Less Mode."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Veuillez vérifier que votre fichier de Pairing est valide, que votre VPN de loopback est activé et que vous êtes connecté à un réseau Wi-Fi stable.\n\nVous pouvez utiliser le navigateur sans JIT temporairement jusqu'au prochain démarrage en activant le mode JITless."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "请检查配对文件是否有效、环回 VPN 是否已打开，以及是否已连接到稳定的无线局域网。\n\n在下次启动前，你可以通过启用无 JIT 模式，暂时在不使用 JIT 的情况下使用浏览器。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
