    "The required Developer Disk Image files for enabling JIT were not found.\n\nJIT has been disabled. Quit the app using the button below, then re-enable JIT from the browser settings." : {
      "comment" : "Paragraph break intentional",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The required Developer Disk Image files for enabling JIT were not found.\n\nJIT has been disabled. Quit the app using the button below, then re-enable JIT from the browser settings."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Les fichiers d'Image Disque de développeur nécessaires ont l'activation du JIT sont introuvables. \n\nLe JIT a été désactivé. Veuillez quitter Reynard en utilisant le bouton ci-dessous, puis réactivez le JIT depuis les paramètres du navigateur."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "未找到启用 JIT 所需的“开发者磁盘映像”文件。\n\nJIT 已停用。请使用下方按钮退出 App，然后在浏览器设置中重新启用 JIT。"
          }
        }
      }
